            <b>SUPA DUPA SUPA PUNK</b>
            (a.k.a.
            <b>SDSP</b>) is a Toronto-based high-volume, high-energy, indie band performing original music since mid-2025. Our sound
                blends post-punk, grunge, garage rock, and blues. We draw inspiration from bands like DFA 1979, Nine Inch Nails, The
                Black Keys, and The White Stripes. We distinguish our heavy, riff-driven songs by incorporating unexpected blues
                elements, specifically harmonica and banjo, to create a fun, engaging, and high-energy live show.
            <br>
                <br>
                    SDSP just recently released their first EP, "SDSP", on May 14th, 2026. It is available on all streaming
                    platforms.
